trans-unit.source: Represents a response of a <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerar ett svar på en <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: When you use the pack URI protocol, you can reference a package and its part elements either locally from inside a package or externally from a Web source.
trans-unit.target: När du använder pack URI-protokollet kan referera du till ett paket och en del element antingen lokalt från i ett paket eller externt från en webbadress.

trans-unit.source: For the pack URI protocol, the forward-slash characters (//) of an embedded [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] are represented by commas (,,).
trans-unit.target: För pack URI-protokollet tecknen snedstreck (/ /) av ett inbäddat [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] representeras av kommatecken (,).

trans-unit.source: For example: `pack://http:,,www.adatum.com,folder,file.package/images/picture1.jpg` references the file `/images/picture1.jpg` that is contained in `http://www.adatum.com/folder/file.package`.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel: `pack://http:,,www.adatum.com,folder,file.package/images/picture1.jpg` refererar till filen `/images/picture1.jpg` som ingår i `http://www.adatum.com/folder/file.package`.

trans-unit.source: Closes the stream for this request.
trans-unit.target: Stänger dataströmmen för denna begäran.

trans-unit.source: Make certain that objects close when they are no longer in use so that resources are not exhausted.
trans-unit.target: Se till att objekt stängs när de inte längre används så att resurser inte har tömts.

trans-unit.source: Gets the content length of the response.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den maximala längden i svaret.

trans-unit.source: The content length, in bytes.
trans-unit.target: Innehåll längden i byte.

trans-unit.source: Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-mime-md.md)] content type of the response stream's content.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-mime-md.md)] innehållstyp för svar-strömma innehåll.

trans-unit.source: If a request does not specify a part in the package, it returns the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] type of the package.
trans-unit.target: Om en begäran inte anger en del i paketet, returnerar den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] typ av paketet.

trans-unit.source: Requests that specify a part in the package return one of the following: 1.
trans-unit.target: Begäranden som anger en del i paketet returnerar något av följande: 1.

trans-unit.source: If the requested part contains a <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A> value, the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A> value is returned.
trans-unit.target: Om den begärda delen innehåller ett <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>värde, den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>returneras värdet.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the requested part contains no <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A> value but the stream name contains a recognized [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] extension type, the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] type corresponding to the extension is returned.
trans-unit.target: Om den begärda delen ingen innehåller <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>värde men stream-namnet innehåller ett okänt [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] tilläggstypen, den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] typ som motsvarar tillägget returneras.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the requested part does not contain a <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A> value nor a recognized [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] extension type, ContentType returns an empty string.
trans-unit.target: Om den begärda delen inte innehåller en <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>värde eller en känd [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] tilläggstypen, ContentType returneras en tom sträng.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart.ContentType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] type of the stream's content.
trans-unit.target: Den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-mime-md.md)] dataströmmens innehållstyp.

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som ska läggas till.

trans-unit.source: Gets the response stream that is contained in the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar svarsdataströmmen som ingår i den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The response stream.
trans-unit.target: Svarsdataströmmen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of Web <xref:System.Net.WebResponse.Headers*> for this response.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar mängden Web <xref:System.Net.WebResponse.Headers*>för det här svaret.</xref:System.Net.WebResponse.Headers*>

trans-unit.source: The collection of Web response <xref:System.Net.WebResponse.Headers*>.
trans-unit.target: Insamling av Webbsvar <xref:System.Net.WebResponse.Headers*>.</xref:System.Net.WebResponse.Headers*>

trans-unit.source: Gets the inner <xref:System.Net.WebResponse> object for the response.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar inre <xref:System.Net.WebResponse>objekt för svaret.</xref:System.Net.WebResponse>

trans-unit.source: InnerResponse returns `null` when the response is from the package cache (when <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse.IsFromCache%2A> is `true`).
trans-unit.target: Returnerar InnerResponse `null` när svaret kommer från paketcachen (när <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse.IsFromCache%2A>är `true`).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse.IsFromCache%2A>

trans-unit.source: The response data as a <xref:System.Net.WebResponse>.
trans-unit.target: Svarsdata som <xref:System.Net.WebResponse>.</xref:System.Net.WebResponse>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the response is from the package cache or from a Web request.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ett värde som anger om svaret är från paketcachen eller från en webbegäran.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the response is from the package cache; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if the response is from a Web request.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om svaret är från paketcachen; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> om svaret kommer från en webbegäran.

trans-unit.source: Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] of the response.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] i svaret.

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the response.
trans-unit.target: Den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] i svaret.
